{"tid":2517392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為撿家人手機翻越護欄 中國遊客墜落身亡","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:10:45.000Z","uid":276273,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"153ef742fca0081d8e7b91143d56e347a8a1f778","tid":2517392,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3521850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3521850&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=d5429405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3521850&h=63291a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3521850</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/05/05 16:38  <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國沂蒙山銀座天蒙旅遊區近日發生一起意外，一名遊客為了撿起家人不慎掉落至步道護欄外的手機，竟不顧告示直接翻越護欄，最後失足墜落身亡，釀成憾事。事發後當地警方隨即介入調查，而目前官方還在進行相關善後工作。<br />\n綜合中媒報導，中國山東省費縣沂蒙山銀座天蒙旅遊區5月2日下午1點多發生遊客墜落意外，一名遊客和家人到該地遊覽時，家人手機掉出步道護欄外，為了將其撿起，這名遊客不顧安全告示便逕自翻越護欄。<br />\n沒想到這名遊客一不小心，就這樣失足墜落，最後不治身亡，旅遊區官方4日通報此消息，並強調事發第一時間，官方便啟動應急方案進行救助，警方也隨即介入此案，目前相關善後工作還在進行中。"},{"pid":"1e547660ccbf933c6bd9417e76c1d56cf44d8604","tid":2517392,"uid":2889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"重刷首抽"},{"pid":"1e69664b3f6943544a0c23de6e316a8b22a72c7e","tid":2517392,"uid":174060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmViN9gsiVpuTYfgaaBTV6uE8CJkyhvAtgUeGCB3tbNGxH?filename=hnLDu2W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhnLDu2W.gif&h=6b41be2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"843c94ac18f99fa0ce9b65ca952022ec46a9920f","tid":2517392,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"護欄太矮 , 旅遊區要賠錢了"},{"pid":"3845be7f4b2d3efb88a6f7dc4893fbfc0a9c1e45","tid":2517392,"uid"